I'm looking to any Frank Owen T206 (had to be a White Sox player). Here are the backs for this card:

El Principe De Gales
Hindu (Brown)
Old Mill
Piedmont - Series 150
Piedmont - Series 350

Looking for cards in Poor to Good condition. Prefer SGC graded, however I would also be interested in raw and PSA graded.

Please let me know what you have and how much, please include shipping charges in prices.

Thanks,
